These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, baking
The people have 2 different jobs:  lawyer, firefighter
1. the lawyer is in an even position##4
2. the firefighter is the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | baking | photography |
| Job     | firefighter    | lawyer   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is skiing is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | 7up | milk        |
| Sport      | skiing  | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, salsa
There are 2 different nationalities: american, pakistani
1. the american is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | reggae |
| Nationality   | american | pakistani |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, kale
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person eating kale is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | mirinda      | hot-chocolate |
| Food       | pineapple | kale    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
