The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, golf
1. the british is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the dutch##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Nationality   | british | dutch   |
| Sport         | surfing | golf |

